com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.outputs

Class SliceSegmentingOutputWriter<O,WriterT extends OutputWriter<O>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.OutputWriter<O>
      • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.outputs.SliceSegmentingOutputWriter<O,WriterT>
  • Type Parameters:
    O - type of values accepted by this output
    WriterT - type of the output writer being written to
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public abstract class SliceSegmentingOutputWriter<O,WriterT extends OutputWriter<O>>
extends OutputWriter<O>
    Segments data by using a separate writer for each slice. This is used by the Sort output so that there can be multiple sorted files per reducer.
